🧠 PrepBuddy – Your Ultimate Placement Prep Partner
PrepBuddy is a powerful placement preparation platform designed to help students crack aptitude rounds of top tech companies. With 25+ company-specific aptitude questions, competitive rankings, and features like DP upload, it’s your all-in-one practice arena!

👉 Click here to access PrepBuddy

🌟 Features
🎯 Aptitude Tests – Curated question sets modeled on real company patterns.

🧑‍🎓 Leaderboard & Rankings – See where you stand among fellow aspirants.

📸 Profile Picture Upload – Upload/display your DP using Cloudinary.

🔐 Gmail Login – Secure authentication via Firebase.

📈 Performance Insights – Track your total points and attempts.

🏅 Achievement Badges – Unlock badges as you progress and excel.

🚀 Tech Stack
Frontend

React + Vite (TypeScript)

Tailwind CSS

ShadCN/UI + Lucide Icons

Axios

Backend

Node.js + Express.js

MongoDB + Mongoose

Firebase Authentication

Cloudinary + Multer

🏷️ Badges
React • Node.js • MongoDB • Firebase • Cloudinary • Open Source • Made with ❤️

